illed-by-new-album-can-we-please-have-fun-3595001">弗洛维尔最近解释说，他对这张唱片感到“完全满足”</a> 。他还在一份声明中表示，这是“他参与过的最令人愉快的唱片”。</p><p> Kings Of Leon 将于今年晚些时候开始一系列<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kings-of-leon-announce-further-2024-uk-and-ireland-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3591919">英国/爱尔兰</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kings-of-leon-announce-2024-world-tour-dates-in-london-and-north-america-3591521">北美巡演</a>，其中包括在伦敦<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/british-summer-time-bst-festival">BST 海德公园 2024</a>举行的头条表演。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/kings-of-leon-tickets/artist/862453?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=wwEzBLW-RxyPWNIXqSXj8x-BUkHUuy3%3AiX3SU00&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此查找任何剩余门票（英国/爱尔兰）</a> 。</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kings-of-leons-rousing-performance-of-mustang-on-fallon-3593471">KOL 今年早些时候在<i>吉米·法伦主演的《今夜秀》</i>的一集中现场表演了《野马》</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kings-of-leon-announce-live-at-wrexham-bonus-version-of-new-album-3751422">Kings Of Leon 宣布新专辑“Live At Wrexham”附赠版本</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
